-- Burger King begins rolling out trans fat-free oil
-- 
-- Fri Jul 6, 2007 7:23am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/06/businesspro-burgerking-transfatfree-dc-idUSWNAS536720070706

 

 (Reuters) - Burger King Corp. BKC.N said it has begun 
rolling out a trans fat-free cooking oil to its restaurants in 
the United States. 

  The world's No.2 hamburger chain said in a statement that 
it expects every U.S. restaurant will be using trans fat-free 
oil by the end of 2008.  (Reporting by Bhaswati Mukhopadhyay in Bangalore)